description: Submission of Reserved Matters in respect of Access, Appearance, Landscaping, Layout and Scale for Phase 3 ( Development Zone D) pursuant to outline permission 2011/0734 dated 30/03/2012 (as amended by application 2013/4025) comprising details of 1 x ground plus 15 storey tower and 1 x ground plus 19 storey tower to provide 198 residential units (18 x studio apartments, 84 x 1 bed, 84 x 2 bed, 12 x 3 bed) together with 225sqm Class A3 (restaurants and cafes), 39 basement level car parking spaces, roof terraces, landscaped mound and play area.
